data.description: Hideaway in your own gated sanctuary in the woods! This private 2BD/3BA home features a wheelchair accessible ramp and driveway access to the top and bottom floors! Bedrooms are located on the main floor in addition to 1 full bath with large kitchen and living room with gas fireplace. The finished basement offers flex and bonus spaces along with 2 full baths featuring a walk-in shower! Outdoor spaces include a fenced yard with a fire pit with plenty of tree coverage for shade! Weather you are cozying-up to the fireplace in the winter or kicking back on your covered porch to watch the fireflies, this roomy home has everything you need to acclimate to mountain time! A new survey of the property has recently been completed! FIBER OPTIC has been installed!
